data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bedroom home located on a beautiful .63 acre lot! Home is handicap accessible with a ramp and all living facilities on 1 level. The lower level has a second kitchen! Great opportunity for a rental or in-law suite. This home also features a large window filled 4 season porch and a big deck. The treed filled yard offers peace and privacy. Located close to town with tons of shopping, restaurants, and so much more! A must see!
